.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-FORWARD-STATS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-forward-stats \- show forwarding payment statistics
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-forward-stats
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns counts of total, settled, and failed forwards along with total fee earned.
.PP
Output: JSON object with total, settled, failed, total_fee_msat.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-fee-revenue (1),
.BR lightning-channel-last-forward (1)
